<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?>
<BES xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="BES.xsd">
	<Analysis>
		<Title>ServerMon: URL Check Results</Title>
		<Description><![CDATA[
<p>Reads back the URL check results reported by the
<a href="https://github.com/jgstew/bigfix-proxyagent-servermon">bigfix-proxyagent-servermon</a>
Management Extender plugin.</p>
<p>Only relevant on proxied devices reported by the servermon plugin: the first
relevance clause is false on ordinary BES clients (and short-circuits, so the
plugin-specific inspectors are never evaluated there), and the second clause
only evaluates true where the inspectors from
<code>Inspectors/servermon.inspectors</code> are defined.</p>
<p><code>HTTP Response Code</code> is <code>0</code> when no HTTP response was
received at all (DNS, TCP, TLS, or timeout failure); see
<code>HTTP Check Result</code> for the reason.</p>
<p><code>HTTP Check Last Error</code> / <code>HTTP Check Last Error Time</code>
record the most recent failed check. The plugin remembers each device's last
error in a local state file and re-sends it with every report, so transient
errors stay visible after they clear, until the next error replaces them.
These properties read "no error recorded" for a device that has never failed.</p>
]]></Description>
		<Relevance>in proxy agent context</Relevance>
		<Relevance>exists servermon version</Relevance>
		<Source>bigfix-proxyagent-servermon</Source>
		<SourceReleaseDate>2026-07-16</SourceReleaseDate>
		<MIMEField>
			<Name>x-fixlet-modification-time</Name>
			<Value>Thu, 16 Jul 2026 18:30:00 +0000</Value>
		</MIMEField>
		<Domain>BESC</Domain>
		<Property Name="URL" ID="1"><![CDATA[url]]></Property>
		<Property Name="HTTP Response Code" ID="2"><![CDATA[http response code]]></Property>
		<Property Name="HTTP Check Result" ID="3"><![CDATA[http check result]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Check Success" ID="4"><![CDATA[check success]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Match Found" ID="5"><![CDATA[if exists match found then (match found) as string else "no match configured"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Response Time (ms)" ID="6"><![CDATA[response time ms]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Last Check Time" ID="7"><![CDATA[last check time]]></Property>
		<Property Name="Last Check Time - As Time" ID="8"><![CDATA[(last check time) as time]]></Property>
		<Property Name="ServerMon Version" ID="9"><![CDATA[servermon version]]></Property>
		<Property Name="HTTP Check Last Error" ID="10"><![CDATA[if exists http check last error then http check last error else "no error recorded"]]></Property>
		<Property Name="HTTP Check Last Error Time" ID="11"><![CDATA[if exists http check last error time then http check last error time else "no error recorded"]]></Property>
	</Analysis>
</BES>
